undaries of race religion and nationality and seeing one in all.\\u00a0Our mission is to provide free, high quality, and compassionate medical care to the underprivileged communities in Malaysia who have poor access to healthcare.\\u00a0<\\/p>\",\"text_color\":\"#121212\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Roboto\",\"typography_font_weight\":\"400\",\"_animation\":\"fadeIn\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"707baf9\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"0c60c7c\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"a49e5db\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"space\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":104,\"sizes\":[]}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"spacer\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"7b23689\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"b29e51d\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"5aedc92\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"Our Future Plans\",\"align\":\"center\",\"_margin\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"15\",\"right\":\"15\",\"bottom\":\"15\",\"left\":\"15\",\"isLinked\":true},\"_animation\":\"fadeInDown\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"30c7ad3\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"58998f9\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"c0a0caf\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"eael_adv_tabs_tab\":[{\"eael_adv_tabs_tab_title\":\"Healthcare awareness\",\"_id\":\"364e393\",\"eael_adv_tabs_tab_show_as_default\":\"inactive\",\"eael_adv_tabs_icon_type\":\"icon\",\"eael_adv_tabs_tab_title_icon_new\":{\"value\":\"fas fa-heartbeat\",\"library\":\"fa-solid\"},\"eael_adv_tabs_tab_title_image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/A2\\/wp-content\\/plugins\\/elementor\\/assets\\/images\\/placeholder.png\"},\"eael_adv_tabs_text_type\":\"content\",\"eael_adv_tabs_tab_content\":\"<h5>Systematic health talks will be conducted in batches for all patients who visit medical camps, with the sole purpose of uplifting health awareness<\\/h5>\"},{\"eael_adv_tabs_tab_title\":\"Ophthalmology\",\"_id\":\"c162606\",\"eael_adv_tabs_tab_show_as_default\":\"inactive\",\"eael_adv_tabs_icon_type\":\"icon\",\"eael_adv_tabs_tab_title_icon_new\":{\"value\":\"far fa-eye\",\"library\":\"fa-regular\"},\"eael_adv_tabs_tab_title_image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/A2\\/wp-content\\/plugins\\/elementor\\/assets\\/images\\/placeholder.png\"},\"eael_adv_tabs_text_type\":\"content\",\"eael_adv_tabs_tab_content\":\"<h5>To get a team of ophthalmologists to help assess and screen patients with diabetic retinopathy, glaucoma, cataract and refractions, and engage in education and early intervention. Future equipment: A slit lamp.<\\/h5>\"},{\"eael_adv_tabs_tab_title\":\"Mobile pathology\",\"_id\":\"d765864\",\"eael_adv_tabs_tab_show_as_default\":\"inactive\",\"eael_adv_tabs_icon_type\":\"icon\",\"eael_adv_tabs_tab_title_icon_new\":{\"value\":\"fab fa-accessible-icon\",\"library\":\"fa-brands\"},\"eael_adv_tabs_tab_title_image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/A2\\/wp-content\\/plugins\\/elementor\\/assets\\/images\\/placeholder.png\"},\"eael_adv_tabs_text_type\":\"content\",\"eael_adv_tabs_tab_content\":\"<h5>A portable laboratory to provide value in our screening and help detect nutritional anaemias, chronic infections, renal diseases, cholesterol issues and complications of lifestyle disease. Once detected, emphasis is on education and early intervention. Future equipment: A mobile lab.<\\/h5>\"},{\"eael_adv_tabs_tab_show_as_default\":\"inactive\",\"eael_adv_tabs_icon_type\":\"icon\",\"eael_adv_tabs_tab_title_icon_new\":{\"value\":\"fas fa-wifi\",\"library\":\"fa-solid\"},\"eael_adv_tabs_tab_title_image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/