als ranging from doctors, dentists, nurses, pharmacists, physiotherapists, nutritionists, counsellors and medical\\/dental students. Our sole purpose is to work with different groups from all over Malaysia, to provide quality medical screening and care for the needy and unfortunate irrespective of race, religion or nationality.<\\/p><p>Our team of committed healthcare professionals will work together to form a structured medical camp with emphasis on patient health and general well-being. The main emphasis is focused on health education and screening for early intervention to prevent complications.<br \\/>In addition to the services provided, we try to actively look out for the very poor and destitute who are in need of medical\\/financial welfare, and sponsorship for the needy is provided from time to time. If there are available volunteers, physiotherapy is offered on an ad-hoc basis, especially to the abandoned elderly who often visit due to chronic aches and pains. <br \\/>Volunteers for this medical project come from diverse backgrounds all over Malaysia and Singapore, and they work hand in hand with the diligent volunteers from Sai Ananda Foundation. Everyone who joins in is reminded before every camp that compassion for suffering and love for everyone irrespective of race religion position or nationality are the only necessary ingredients to make this service project a success.<\\/p>\",\"align\":\"justify\",\"text_color\":\"#202020\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"b819658\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":900,\"sizes\":[]}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"3ab318c\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"51742da\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"Why did we form this portal?\",\"header_size\":\"h1\",\"align\":\"center\",\"title_color\":\"#000000\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Arial\",\"typography_font_weight\":\"500\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"},{\"id\":\"bb15162\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/A2\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2020\\/09\\/Kerling-pic06.jpg\",\"id\":79},\"image_size\":\"custom\",\"image_custom_dimension\":{\"width\":\"1024\",\"height\":\"300\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"},{\"id\":\"e239411\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>One of the challenges we faced during each medical camp is inadequate medical and dental volunteers. This is the reason why we are linking up healthcare professionals all around Malaysia and the Asia Pacific region through this universal portal called Doctors Connect. We also aim to work with other countries to expand our pool of resources, so that we can do much more for the society collectively.<\\/p><p>The other reason for forming this portal is to assure all healthcare professionals who have volunteered here, that the medical camps we host will be of a certain standard. Medical camps here are mainly organised by doctors, as we aim to use our experience to provide the maximal benefit to the poor and needy patients.<\\/p><p>We hope to increase our volunteers base in Malaysia by 50% through this new portal and hope to conduct one medical camp per month from the current once in two or three months.<\\/p><p>For doctors, a well-run medical camp is like dining at a good restaurant, chances to come back are high if the food is good. Therefore, all our events are carefully planned in advance by our medical and non-medical think-tank team, to ensure we select the right area that is genuinely in need of help, and deliver what is appropriately needed to them. In the end, it should be a win-win situation for everyone, as our patients and our volunteers should feel happy and good after every camp.<\\/p><p>If we can work together despite all our differences, to reach out and help the poor and needy, then this effort to unite people through Doctors Connect will truly be a worthwhile cause. And in return, we should feel good after every event and eventually transform to become better individuals in time to come, which is the ultimate objective of these events.<\\/p><p>Please feel free to provide any suggestions for improvement or if you know of any areas that are in need of dire medical care. Also, we hope to keep you interested and motivated as time goes by, but at any time if you have to leave the group due to personal reasons, please do so, no hard feelings at all. There will be absolutely no reasons or apologies needed, and we wish you only the very best.<\\/p><p>Once again, it\\u2019s truly a privilege to know each of you, and we hope to do some good work with all of you at some point in time.<\\/p>\",\"align\":\"justify\",\"text_color\":\"#202020\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"bd2e430\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"padding\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"50\",\"right\":\"50\",\"bottom\":\"50\",\"left\":\"50\",\"isLinked\":true},\"html_tag\":\"div\",\"background_overlay_background\":\"classic\",\"background_overlay_image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/A2\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2020\\/09\\/antibiotics-1782433-scaled.jpg\",\"id\":116},\"background_overlay_position\":\"center center\",\"background_overlay_attachment\":\"scroll\",\"background_overlay_repeat\":\"no-repeat\",\"background_overlay_size\":\"cover\",\"background_overlay_opacity\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":0.55,\"sizes\":[]},\"background_overlay_hover_image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/A2\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2020\\/09\\/business-3362081_1920.jpg\",\"id\":41}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"290cf18\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"652083e\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"text\":\"Become Volunteers\",\"align\":\"center